caption:
“Divine Order” | 18x18 | Collage on Panel - now showing @garnernarrative in my solo exhibition. The opening reception is Sunday 5/18 from 2-5PM, with an artist discussion at 3:30. Hope you’ll stop by!

“Many of these pieces reflect my feelings about the confines of the Christian religion and meanings placed on religious iconography. The pieces with women in those spaces are a reaction against the role women are expected to have in the church.“
